Unit trusts                   -9.0  18.2   7.8
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Japan:
Investment trusts             -4.4  14.8  93.2
Unit trusts                  -21.7  -2.3  77.3
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Europe:
Investment trusts            -12.5  64.1  52.9
Unit trusts                  -15.6  40.0  46.2
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Figures are % growth. Investment trust figures are mid-price to
mid-price, income reinvested. Unit trust figures are offer-to-bid,
income reinvested. Note: this implies a slight bias against unit
trusts.
